15:20.653 --> 15:25.420
♪ When I wake in the morning ♪

15:25.558 --> 15:31.327
♪ And when I'm sleeping
in the evening ♪

15:32.932 --> 15:39.565
♪ All my thoughts are
about you ♪

15:39.705 --> 15:46.634
♪ And all the things you
bring to me ♪

15:46.779 --> 15:50.215
♪ Life has finally gone my way ♪

15:50.349 --> 15:53.876
♪ I prayed that we would meet ♪

15:54.020 --> 15:56.955
♪ Love you more
and more each day ♪

15:57.089 --> 16:00.650
♪ I find myself complete ♪

16:00.793 --> 16:04.161
♪ Every hour, every day ♪

16:04.297 --> 16:07.528
♪ You feel my love inside ♪

16:07.667 --> 16:11.194
♪ We stand together honestly ♪

16:11.337 --> 16:13.669
♪ 'Cause through it all ♪

16:13.806 --> 16:15.137
♪ Through it all ♪

16:15.274 --> 16:17.971
♪ Through it all... ♪

16:18.110 --> 16:22.604
♪ Love survives ♪

